OL,6,FEthical recruitment from abroad is
OL,7,Fpart of the Welsh Government's plan to
OL,8,Fincrease the workforce in the NHS.
OL,10,FMore than 400 internationally educated
OL,11,Fnurses were employed from overseas
OL,12,Flast year.
